name: GOGO's LAB
description: R.O.B got an emergency call from GOGO, looks like someone has broke into the lab. When they arrived, the situation is critical! Mythic GOGO is escaping, missing pod, fire and power failure. R.O.B and Bots helping them to save this situation. R.O.B is even risking his life transferring his own energy to turn on the lab's electrical power so that the process can continue. Will they succeed helping GOGO's secret mission to release 5555 GOGOS data safely to the world?
